node.text:
These couldn’t have arrived at a better time! I’ve been doing more outdoor Circuit Breaker running and I appreciate the thumping beats and Active Noise Cancelling from the new Sudio Ett wireless earbuds. I especially love little details like the changeable eartips so that they fit snugly and securely during the runs (my previous earphones kept falling out mid run and it was sooo disruptive). 🏃🏻‍♂️ .
Sudio is now running (pun intended)  a Hari Raya promo with a 15% discount (code: RAYA2020) and there’s free worldwide shipping and a cool tote bag thrown in 💪🏻 www.sudio.com
